lab.android.rwth.evgenijandkate.plugscontrolclient.model

Class PlugTransferableData

  • java.lang.Object
    • lab.android.rwth.evgenijandkate.plugscontrolclient.model.PlugTransferableData

  • public class PlugTransferableData
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by elobanova on 07.06.2015. A class representing the object for storing the plugs data in order to transfer it to the server, when the user with the administrative rights is adding a new plug. He can specify the plug/s human readable name, a switch code, a house code and the state in which the plug is initially.
